CONTEXT CompositionISAendoSuperUnrelated IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT CompositionISAendoSuperUnrelated
{+ Test composition with ISA hierarchy: endorelation on supertype to unrelated.
   Given A ISA B, test r[B*B];s[C*Z] where join(B,C) doesn't exist (C is unrelated).
   This should FAIL because the type checker cannot find a join. +}

CLASSIFY A ISA B

RELATION r[B*B]
RELATION s[C*Z]
RELATION result[B*Z]

RULE testCompositionISAFail: result = r;s

ENDCONTEXT
